        <p>Study of traffic flow, control systems, and management strategies for efficient transportation.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Traffic flow theory</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Signal design</li><br>
