  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Core Concepts</h2>
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Traffic Flow Theory</div>
        <p>Understand the principles of traffic flow, capacity analysis, and level of service concepts.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://ops.fhwa.dot.gov/trafficanalysistools/index.htm" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Geometric Design</div>
        <p>Master the fundamentals of roadway alignment, cross-section design, and intersection geometry.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://highways.dot.gov/safety/proven-safety-countermeasures/geometric-design" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Pavement Design</div>
        <p>Learn about flexible and rigid pavement design, materials, and performance evaluation.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.fhwa.dot.gov/pavement/design.cfm" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Traffic Safety</div>
        <p>Study crash analysis, safety countermeasures, and road safety audits.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://safety.fhwa.dot.gov/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Transportation Planning</div>
        <p>Understand travel demand modeling, forecasting, and transportation system planning.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.planning.dot.gov/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Public Transportation</div>
        <p>Learn about transit planning, operations, and management principles.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.transit.dot.gov/research-innovation" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Traffic Signal Design</div>
        <p>Study signal timing, coordination, and adaptive control systems.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://ops.fhwa.dot.gov/arterial_mgmt/traffic_sig.htm" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Intelligent Transportation Systems</div>
        <p>Explore advanced technologies for improving transportation safety and efficiency.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.its.dot.gov/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Transportation Economics</div>
        <p>Master benefit-cost analysis, project evaluation, and transportation financing.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.transportation.gov/transportation-policy/transportation-and-economy" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Airport Planning & Design</div>
        <p>Learn techniques for airport layout, airside and landside facilities design.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.faa.gov/airports/resources/advisory_circulars/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Sustainable Transportation</div>
        <p>Study environmentally friendly transportation systems and green infrastructure.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.transportation.gov/sustainability" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Transportation Data Analysis</div>
        <p>Understand statistical methods, big data applications, and transportation modeling.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.bts.gov/learn-about-bts-and-our-work" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Complete Streets</div>
        <p>Explore design approaches that accommodate all road users safely and efficiently.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://highways.dot.gov/complete-streets" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Freight Transportation</div>
        <p>Learn about logistics, supply chain management, and freight planning.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://ops.fhwa.dot.gov/freight/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Transportation Equity</div>
        <p>Study accessibility, environmental justice, and inclusive transportation planning.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.transportation.gov/equity-Justice40" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  

